OL,3,C'Social media ruined my life' says
OL,4,Cteen amid calls for online child safety
OL,6,FA 17-year-old girl says that a social
OL,7,Fmedia ban for children under 16 would
OL,8,F"be best for young people" after she
OL,9,Fsays it "ruined her life".
OL,11,FJorja Edwards from Blaenau Ffestiniog
OL,12,Fwas just 13 years old when intimate
OL,13,Fpictures of herself were shared
OL,14,Fonline. In 2022, she had an account on
OL,15,Fthe social media app Snapchat and
OL,16,Fstruck up a friendship with a
OL,17,Fstranger, a boy she believed was 14.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
