PN,46202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1772457071
OL,3,C'Social media ruined my life' says
OL,4,Cteen amid calls for online child safety
OL,6,FAfter talking every day for three
OL,7,Fmonths, they shared intimate pictures
OL,8,Fof themselves with each other. She
OL,9,Fasked him not to share them with
OL,10,Fanyone else. But following an
OL,11,Fargument, the boy circulated her
OL,12,Fpictures in group chats full of
OL,13,Fstrangers, as well as pupils from
OL,14,FJorja's school.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1772457071
OL,3,C'Social media ruined my life' says
OL,4,Cteen amid calls for online child safety
OL,6,F"I thought he wouldn't do such a
OL,7,Fthing, but he did," says Jorja. "I
OL,8,Fjust felt really disgusted in myself.
OL,9,FI locked myself away and refused to go
OL,10,Fto school just so I wouldn't have to
OL,11,Fsit in lessons and get people bringing
OL,12,Fup the pictures and sexualising the
OL,13,Fpictures."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1772457071
OL,3,C'Social media ruined my life' says
OL,4,Cteen amid calls for online child safety
OL,6,FShe told S4C's current affairs
OL,7,Fprogramme, Y Byd ar Bedwar, that the
OL,8,Fexperience is one that put her in a
OL,9,F"really dark place". The case was
OL,10,Freferred to the police, who confirmed
OL,11,Fthat the boy was under 16 at the time;
OL,12,Fbecause of that, no criminal action
OL,13,Fwas taken and both parties received
OL,14,Fsupport.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
