FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1772457071
OL,3,C'Social media ruined my life' says
OL,4,Cteen amid calls for online child safety
OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said: "These
OL,7,Fhorrific stories are precisely why we
OL,8,Fare going further and faster to
OL,9,Fprotect children online. We've
OL,10,Fannounced new measures that will
OL,11,Frequire platforms to take down
OL,12,Fintimate images shared without a
OL,13,Fvictim's consent within 48 hours of
OL,14,Fbeing reported. We have already
OL,15,Fintroduced some of the strongest
OL,16,Fonline safety protections in the
OL,17,Fworld, requiring platforms to remove
OL,18,Fharmful content, but we know this is
OL,19,Fnot enough on its own."
OL,26,@nD@aOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/10
