OL,3,C'Social media ruined my life' says
OL,4,Cteen amid calls for online child safety
OL,6,FFor Jorja, a ban is something she
OL,7,Fwelcomes. "Social media these days is
OL,8,Fnot safe for children under the age of
OL,9,F16."
OL,11,F"It's destroyed my life as a teenager,
OL,12,Fand it's what's best for young
OL,13,Fchildren so that they don't have to go
OL,14,Fthrough what I did."
OL,16,FWatch 'Y Byd ar Bedwar: Y Genhedlaeth
OL,17,FGaeth', Monday at 8pm on S4C, S4C
OL,18,FClic, and BBC iPlayer. English
OL,19,Fsubtitles are available.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/10
